:TechnicalMinimum a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf saref:Property ; rdfs:label "Technical Minimum"@en .
:AverageCost a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf saref:Property ; rdfs:label "Average Cost"@en .
:StatusOffOn a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf saref:Property ; rdfs:label "Status (0-off / 1-on)"@en .
:Inertia a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf saref:Property ; rdfs:label "Inertia (H)"@en .
